{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":73333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[32],"categories_output":[{"ID":32,"slug":"%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1%e6%b4%9e%e5%af%9f","name":"设计洞察","term_taxonomy_id":32,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":42}],"tags":[70,58,71],"tags_output":[{"ID":70,"slug":"%e6%80%9d%e7%bb%b4%e8%83%bd%e5%8a%9b","name":"思维能力","term_taxonomy_id":70,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":58,"slug":"%e8%89%ba%e6%9c%af%e5%88%9b%e6%84%8f","name":"艺术创意","term_taxonomy_id":58,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":71,"slug":"%e8%bf%90%e8%90%a5%e8%a7%84%e5%88%92","name":"运营规划","term_taxonomy_id":71,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1}],"thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_96ec1fde8931707717acc5a7-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecfdeaccaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_96ec1fde8931707717acc5a7-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecfdeaccaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_96ec1fde8931707717acc5a7-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecfdeaccaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_full":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_96ec1fde8931707717acc5a7-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecfdeaccaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"date_day":"03","date_month":"08","date_month_e":"August","date_year":"2011","date_weekday":"Wednesday","title":"做创意的实施行为-培养自己的创意思维和设计能力","excerpt":"创新和创意是非常难的，哪怕你有很多经验，也不一定能信手拈来，偶尔，也会有一些启发和成功的时候。我把这种机遇记录了下来，下面就聊聊如何才能\"主动\"培养自己的创意思维和设计能力。","content":"<p>每隔一段时间我都要在网页设计的各个方面做一个研究探讨，以提升网页设计水平。</p>\n<p>创新和创意是非常难的，哪怕你有很多经验，也不一定能信手拈来，偶尔，也会有一些启发和成功的时候。我把这种机遇记录了下来，下面就聊聊如何才能\"主动\"培养自己的创意思维和设计能力。</p>\n<p>自己不论做什么项目，或者玩什么游戏，或者绘画，动画还是网站等等，实施创意的方法如下：</p>\n<h4>1. 先找构成“元素”——存在的物体或者需要的东西</h4>\n<h4>2. 然后在纸上写出“元素关键词”——物体或者元素的名称</h4>\n<h4>3. 找元素之间的联系——固有联系和已经存在的联系进行参考</h4>\n<h4>4. 创新“元素关系”——寻找突破口！ 创造合理的新联系，表达中心。</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>可以突破元素本身的特性，使用上述200种创意方法</li>\n<li>可以衍生元素特性，演变原本的固有元素，进行新特性的开发</li>\n<li>可以使用其固有特性创造“非常规”的新联系</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.创新新联系的同时，要找到一条“风格主线”和“头衔事物”——统一整个创意的“领军手法”，不可忽视，具体可以从以下方面着手：</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>找到贯穿整个创意的“主要元素”，由其特性展开联想，或者整个创意都包含它，并且由它带动整个创意的有序运行</li>\n<li>找到整个创意表现的“基本风格”，由表现风格展开创意元素的联系</li>\n<li>找到某个主要事物的“动作、形态特征”，由此进行衍生和展开</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这样就能充分使用自己的大脑去想，利于创意思维的磨练。</p>\n","slug":"7c8689f8afe586b1f9a23d3b","prev":[{"ID":43333,"title":"网页设计之对于风格的探索和见解","excerpt":"每个人都有自己的风格，也有自己真实的水平，也有自己评判自己和他人的标准，但是这些都有一个层面，都有一个针对性，一统江湖只能让你更加不成熟。","slug":"0166368a0d0ce32ae1a22e37","post_date":"2011-06-11 11:14:12","post_date_gmt":"2011-06-11 11:14:12","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_4d9762c23a88cccd7ea4d2d9-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdcacccdeaddxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_4d9762c23a88cccd7ea4d2d9-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdcacccdeaddxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_4d9762c23a88cccd7ea4d2d9-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdcacccdeaddxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":103333,"title":"5年至今，到底有什么一直没变","excerpt":"2007年至今，到底有什么一直没变....","slug":"9088c7a0c717397130871062","post_date":"2011-09-26 01:36:35","post_date_gmt":"2011-09-26 01:36:35","thumbnail":[],"thumbnail_mini":[],"thumbnail_retina":[]}],"post_date":"2011-08-03 23:58:17","post_date_gmt":"2011-08-03 23:58:17","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2022-11-17 02:50:55","post_modified_gmt":"2022-11-17 02:50:55","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"https://matrixflip.com/api/?post_type=post&#038;p=73333","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post